{
  "stem": "5559.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where you get $5, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm just saying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they took advantage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Whatever they came out, they used to sit, used to be a little place there where people used to change.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, what they call here in America free market or something like this?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] change.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "What do you got?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You still have a little ring?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'm going give you one pound of corn meal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So you will have, for two meals, for a little diamond ring, which may be worth two, three, whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "How did your parents manage with the food?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this is the way how you had to manage-- the best you can.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you had to eat, what you call, you get an entree, and you get a first course, the second, the third, like you go to a restaurant.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first course is potato, then the second entree is potato soup, and dessert is another potato.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you get three ways of this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this is how you man-- you imagine things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You feel good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Try a little potato puree, a little mashed potatoes, a little water for the potatoes is potato soup.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Forget about if you think of any meat or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Don't even think about.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were from all over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were from Hungary, from Austria, from Yugoslavia, and of course a lot of Russian Jews, Ukrainian Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're all included.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "However, see, they live over there I don't know how many years, you know, maybe 20, 30, 40, 50.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- Jews, the community as such, they knew how to get around things, because they knew the peasants of the Ukraines.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You follow me?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, I remember, then, we finally moved into a Jew barber.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a barber.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That is funny.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
